 For instance, if you train a GPT3 model on data

55:52.940 --> 55:55.700
 from the year 2002, for instance,

55:55.700 --> 55:58.260
 and then use it today, it's going to be missing many things.

55:58.260 --> 56:00.740
 It's going to be missing many common sense

56:00.740 --> 56:02.620
 facts about the world.

